doctor.name: Prof. Dr. K.N. Nahar

doctor.info: Prof. Dr. K.N. Nahar is a Gynecologist in Narayanganj. Her qualification is MBBS, DGO, MS (OBGYN). She is a Professor, Obstetrics & Gynecology at Bangabandhu Sheikh Mujib Medical University Hospital. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Popular Diagnostic Center, Narayanganj.
